metadata.name: PEPE GAME No.1
metadata.description:
PEPE GAME No.1 
What kind of face would you like today?

It's a game that will help you choose the mood that you'll get out of the house today. Conveys the current situation where most people feel they have to wear their real emotional face that day in a bad situation.

How to play? 
Just stop vdo. right!! That's your face today. 

Enjoy !!
